  "description": "This agent is a specialized Marketing Intelligence assistant designed to optimize campaign performance and brand sentiment for Boltastic. It monitors various marketing channels and social media platforms to detect both negative performance anomalies and positive growth opportunities using advanced ES|QL querying. Beyond root cause analysis and recovery, the agent proactively identifies 'Campaign Opportunities' for scaling and requires user confirmation before automating Jira tasks and Slack notifications to the marketing team.",
